{"tid":1802623,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 應粉絲要求公開小時候的可愛照片","createTime":"2019-12-29T15:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T09:53:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16fa4666ca5f4050f7f64f11c3192f0738a928db","tid":1802623,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"IU 應粉絲要求公開小時候的可愛照片。<br />\n<br />\n27日，IU 在亞洲巡迴演唱會《Love, Poem》最後一站印尼時，進行了 instagram 的互動問答，她寫說：「今晚，我來不是因為我睡不著，而是因為這是這次巡迴最後一站，覺得上床睡覺很可惜，才開始了這個。」<br />\n<br />\n隨後 IU 收到了一系列的問題，包括「能給我們看一張小時候的照片嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n而 IU 真的分享了她小時候的照片回應粉絲，照片如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.kpopn.com/upload/4837a55b42343ddf3894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2Fupload%2F4837a55b42343ddf3894.jpg&h=69867f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你是不是也跟我一樣覺得好可愛？"},{"pid":"f85a323b70388703659dcc6dd0d5d27d3e70aa7e","tid":1802623,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"講係近期影我都信"},{"pid":"6d6cae7e350b1f2aca5ce19ac8c5323611ca183a","tid":1802623,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/bc370de8fa93aa24ea08a0dabe35af36/4917f51f15eb077e-f0/s400x600/f878fa4f05aef9aec4b9c866bae48c7728bc47b3.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fbc370de8fa93aa24ea08a0dabe35af36%2F4917f51f15eb077e-f0%2Fs400x600%2Ff878fa4f05aef9aec4b9c866bae48c7728bc47b3.gifv&h=9b102847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/b5b91313bfc1fee09b0c9b87b078a950/4917f51f15eb077e-f6/s400x600/a9d5908b7a6c41e333f54fbc54d9bc0ccaf75cd4.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fb5b91313bfc1fee09b0c9b87b078a950%2F4917f51f15eb077e-f6%2Fs400x600%2Fa9d5908b7a6c41e333f54fbc54d9bc0ccaf75cd4.gifv&h=a0b7107b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/3f109cc2563a49